It's spelled inside out, it's file!

00:00:09.080 --> 00:00:14.580
Snick Live with Roundhouse, tonight starting at 8-7 Central only on Nickelodeon.

00:00:14.580 --> 00:00:19.580
I wondered about who invented those million little thingamajiggies we use in our daily lives.

00:00:20.580 --> 00:00:22.580
I mean, someone had to think...

