00:06:00.050 --> 00:06:01.050
In the tub?

00:06:01.050 --> 00:06:03.050
See, it displaces a bunch of water,

00:06:03.050 --> 00:06:06.050
so you use less, and you still get a nice full tub.

00:06:06.050 --> 00:06:07.050
Oh, I get you.

00:06:07.050 --> 00:06:10.050
The trouble is, no one wants to take a bath with a brick.

00:06:10.050 --> 00:06:11.050
I'm sorry, Sam.

00:06:11.050 --> 00:06:12.050
Me too.

00:06:12.050 --> 00:06:14.050
People are so lacking in vision.

00:06:14.050 --> 00:06:18.050
I wonder if Eli Whitney had this problem with the cotton gin.

00:06:18.050 --> 00:06:20.050
No, I bet they loved him.

00:06:20.050 --> 00:06:23.050
I bet they raved about that stupid cotton gin.

00:06:23.050 --> 00:06:25.050
