00:07:20.050 --> 00:07:22.050
Not in a thousand years.

00:07:22.050 --> 00:07:25.050
Not if my life depended on it. Not a chance.

00:07:25.050 --> 00:07:27.050
What's up?

00:07:27.050 --> 00:07:30.050
Well, Ferguson's gonna have to have his tonsils out.

