But now back to Pete and Pete on Snick.

00:43:53.770 --> 00:43:56.890
It took me exactly three seconds to learn one thing

00:43:56.890 --> 00:43:58.890
about Slern's special project.

00:43:59.930 --> 00:44:02.010
There was nothing special about it.

00:44:03.370 --> 00:44:07.770
Use the chop saw and make me a circular form.

00:44:08.730 --> 00:44:18.570
And this time, Mr. Wrigley, don't cue the edges.

00:44:18.570 --> 00:44:21.450
I had become Slern's personal power tool.

00:44:22.090 --> 00:44:25.690
I sawed, sanded, drilled, hammered.

00:44:26.410 --> 00:44:28.570
Every day my limbs were in danger.

00:44:29.770 --> 00:44:31.850
And if that weren't bad enough,

00:44:31.850 --> 00:44:34.250
Slern never told me what I was working on.

00:44:35.450 --> 00:44:35.770
Never.

00:44:36.730 --> 00:44:39.690
All I knew was that he kept it hidden from the world

00:44:39.690 --> 00:44:41.850
in a cabinet that was never opened.

00:44:43.290 --> 00:44:45.370
No one else seemed too concerned about it.

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:48.170
But no matter how hard I tried,

00:44:48.170 --> 00:44:50.410
I couldn't stop wondering what was in there.

00:44:51.130 --> 00:44:53.210
It was like some black hole

00:44:53.210 --> 00:44:56.490
