00:44:57.450 --> 00:44:58.970
What was Slern hiding?

00:44:59.850 --> 00:45:00.970
What difference does it make?

00:45:00.970 --> 00:45:02.090
It's a special project.

00:45:02.090 --> 00:45:03.530
But don't you think it's a little weird

00:45:03.530 --> 00:45:05.850
