00:45:12.650 --> 00:45:17.050
Maybe it is an anti-ballistic fragmentary explosive.

00:45:17.050 --> 00:45:19.530
I think you're going a little overboard, Pete.

00:45:19.530 --> 00:45:20.570
I don't trust vanilla.

00:45:21.690 --> 00:45:24.250
If the special project wasn't something bad or dangerous,

00:45:24.250 --> 00:45:25.690
why wouldn't he tell me what it is?

00:45:25.690 --> 00:45:27.130
I'm working on it.

00:45:27.130 --> 00:45:28.810
If you're really that worried about it,

00:45:28.810 --> 00:45:30.570
why don't you just ask Mike what it is?

00:45:32.090 --> 00:45:32.730
