00:45:34.330 --> 00:45:34.650
Mike.

00:45:35.850 --> 00:45:36.650
Mike Hellstrom.

00:45:37.530 --> 00:45:40.810
Since when did you start calling endless Mike Mike?

00:45:41.930 --> 00:45:45.210
Whenever I call him Mike, he helps me out.

00:45:55.390 --> 00:45:58.990
Oh boy, that, uh, cross-belt sure does ride like a Cadillac, huh?

00:46:01.500 --> 00:46:03.900
